<p>At the <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/critics-choice-awards-2026-full-winners-list-sinners-adolescence-squid-game-3-and-one-battle-after-another-nab-big-honors-1399656">2026 Critics&#39; Choice Awards</a>, big winners included films Sinners and One Battle After Another, TV show <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/adolescence-is-brad-pitts-production-company-in-talks-with-creators-of-netflix-series-for-possible-season-2-deets-1381631">Adolescence</a>, and, of course, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/timothee-chalamets-outstanding-screen-presence-in-dune-and-a-complete-unknown-earns-him-prestigious-italian-award-1385610">Timoth&eacute;e Chalamet</a>,&nbsp;who is having his grand year of celebrations thanks to his portrayal in Marty Mauser. He added a hint of love to his acceptance speech with a special shoutout to his &lsquo;partner&rsquo;, Kylie Jenner, who had accompanied him to the ceremony. She smiled and reciprocated the confession.&nbsp;</p>

