<p>The vampire theory gained traction because Eddie was killed by bat-like creatures, and bats are closely associated with vampires in pop culture. Fans also pointed to Kas&#39; lore as a possible twist the <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/stranger-things-season-5-release-2025-premiere-of-millie-bobby-brown-starrer-confirmed-by-duffer-brothers-1371381">Duffer Brothers</a> could adapt for the final season.</p>

