<p>Ross Duffer addressed the theory directly in early December 2025, saying, &ldquo;There&rsquo;s some wild theories, even for season 5. Eddie is not a vampire. I will say that much.&rdquo; The statement was meant to shut down speculation, though it hasn&rsquo;t fully stopped fan discussions.</p>

