<p>Dr. Kay was taking Kali&rsquo;s blood to continue Dr. Brenner&rsquo;s experiments, infusing pregnant women in hopes of recreating powers like Eleven&rsquo;s. The show makes it clear that no actual vampires exist in this storyline.</p>
