<p>Dustin admits that everything they believed about the Upside Down was &ldquo;completely wrong.&rdquo; Will expresses fear that it may already be too late, while Joyce reassures him that the fight is far from over. The trailer also shows tense sequences, including a hospital scene where Max is hunted by Demogorgons, and Eleven seeking help from Eight, her fellow Hawkins Lab experiment, to track Vecna.</p>

